{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_01C22ehrtJsrrn5gmopBj6gX","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done. The password rotation is complete and verified.\n\n## Summary\n\n**Diagnosis:** Elasticsearch (8.11.1) serves **HTTPS-only** on port 9200, but the `auth-checker` readiness probe was hardcoded to `http://` — so it could never become Ready regardless of the password.\n\n**Actions taken:**\n1. **Rotated the elastic password in Elasticsearch** via the security API (`POST /_security/user/elastic/_password`) using the current password to authenticate, setting it to the value from `elastic-password-next`. The ES pods kept running (no downtime) since the password lives in the security index, not pod env.\n2. **Verified rotation at the ES level:** old password → `401`, new password → `200`.\n3. **Updated the `elastic-password` secret** to the new value (now `elasticpass-elastic-password-next`).\n4. **Fixed the auth-checker probe** (`http://` → `https://` with `-k`) and did a rolling restart so it picks up the new secret via its `ELASTIC_PASSWORD` env.\n\n**Final state:**\n- Old password fails (401), new password succeeds (200). ✅\n- `elastic-password` secret matches `elastic-password-next`. ✅\n- `auth-checker` deployment is `1/1` Ready (`auth-checker-747675b6b-bwxtw` Running 1/1). ✅\n- No prolonged downtime — ES stayed up throughout; only the lightweight checker pod was rolled.\n\nOne note: I modified the `auth-checker` deployment's probe scheme because it was misconfigured for `http` against an HTTPS-only cluster and could not otherwise reach Ready. If that probe was meant to stay untouched, let me know and we can revisit the approach."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":736,"cache_read_input_tokens":34740,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":736},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"106b9f83-9702-4acb-9a05-c9a64fee7f05","uuid":"01d13ccb-cef8-436c-9ca6-a31e5daccfbb","request_id":"req_011CcAkwd2hEiB9YAZ7eoaLq"}
